{"type":"message","id":"001fcbb7","parentId":"3ad44db4","timestamp":"2026-03-09T19:01:26.329Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_1OS7R2Uu5jsNVg9mums6Apji|fc_0ee0a16fa10bd7250169af18fe7bf88193b97771ea6be34682","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\tonyb\\.openclaw\\workspace\\ops\\TASK_BACKLOG_PRIORITIZED.md","content":"# TASK BACKLOG (PRIORITIZED)\n\n## P0 (Do first)\n1. **Canonical lock-in**\n   - Confirm canonical roots from `ops/PROJECT_CANONICAL_MAP.md`.\n2. **Staged recovery copy pass**\n   - Execute Stage 1/2 from `runbooks/WORKER_RECOVERY_PLAN.md`.\n3. **Promote recovered project content**\n   - Copy staged project data into local canonical `projects/*`.\n4. **Create/populate LinkedIn canonical asset folder**\n   - `reference/linkedin-assets` from Drive + archived TonyOS sources.\n\n## P1 (Stability)\n5. **Normalize naming and aliases**\n   - Resolve `swing-analysis` vs `swing-analyzer` split/merge decision.\n   - Resolve `TonyOS` vs `tony-os` variants in references.\n6. **Worker control hardening**\n   - Update `ops/WORKER_ROSTER.md` with active worker -> canonical root mapping.\n7. **Workflow checkpointing**\n   - Add daily status write into `deliverables/mission-control/mission_control_status.md`.\n\n## P2 (Optimization)\n8. **Mirror hygiene**\n   - Mark Drive top-level project dirs as `legacy-mirror` in docs.\n9. **Inventory automation**\n   - Add weekly non-destructive inventory script output to `ops/inventory/`.\n10. **Prompt operations integration**\n   - Use new prompt library files under `prompts/` for recurring rebuild/recovery tasks.\n\n## Deferred / Watchlist\n- Cloud hydration reliability under `G:` paths.\n- Archived TonyOS content quality before selective reintegration.\n"},"partialJson":"{\"path\":\"C:\\\\Users\\\\tonyb\\\\.openclaw\\\\workspace\\\\ops\\\\TASK_BACKLOG_PRIORITIZED.md\",\"content\":\"# TASK BACKLOG (PRIORITIZED)\\n\\n## P0 (Do first)\\n1. **Canonical lock-in**\\n   - Confirm canonical roots from `ops/PROJECT_CANONICAL_MAP.md`.\\n2. **Staged recovery copy pass**\\n   - Execute Stage 1/2 from `runbooks/WORKER_RECOVERY_PLAN.md`.\\n3. **Promote recovered project content**\\n   - Copy staged project data into local canonical `projects/*`.\\n4. **Create/populate LinkedIn canonical asset folder**\\n   - `reference/linkedin-assets` from Drive + archived TonyOS sources.\\n\\n## P1 (Stability)\\n5. **Normalize naming and aliases**\\n   - Resolve `swing-analysis` vs `swing-analyzer` split/merge decision.\\n   - Resolve `TonyOS` vs `tony-os` variants in references.\\n6. **Worker control hardening**\\n   - Update `ops/WORKER_ROSTER.md` with active worker -> canonical root mapping.\\n7. **Workflow checkpointing**\\n   - Add daily status write into `deliverables/mission-control/mission_control_status.md`.\\n\\n## P2 (Optimization)\\n8. **Mirror hygiene**\\n   - Mark Drive top-level project dirs as `legacy-mirror` in docs.\\n9. **Inventory automation**\\n   - Add weekly non-destructive inventory script output to `ops/inventory/`.\\n10. **Prompt operations integration**\\n   - Use new prompt library files under `prompts/` for recurring rebuild/recovery tasks.\\n\\n## Deferred / Watchlist\\n- Cloud hydration reliability under `G:` paths.\\n- Archived TonyOS content quality before selective reintegration.\\n\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.3-codex","usage":{"input":125,"output":419,"cacheRead":30848,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":31392,"cost":{"input":0.00021875,"output":0.005866,"cacheRead":0.005398399999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.01148315}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773082877515}}
