{"type":"message","id":"45fd658c","parentId":"58d7ebe3","timestamp":"2026-03-09T19:01:37.630Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_sENQKUvk6sXMtKbz3oRQ6l7n|fc_0ee0a16fa10bd7250169af190855f48193a2fdf6ee629d20df","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\tonyb\\.openclaw\\workspace\\runbooks\\WORKFLOW_BLUEPRINT_V1.md","content":"# WORKFLOW BLUEPRINT V1\n\n## Intent\nCreate a repeatable, safe rebuild workflow for project/worker continuity without destructive operations.\n\n## Workflow Graph (V1)\n1. **Inventory (Read-only)**\n   - Scan local + mirrors\n   - Emit inventory report\n2. **Canonical Mapping**\n   - Select canonical roots\n   - Label all duplicates as source/legacy\n3. **Staging Recovery (Copy-only)**\n   - Pull from chosen mirror to staging\n   - Validate file counts and key manifests\n4. **Promotion (Copy-only)**\n   - Copy from staging to canonical project roots\n5. **Worker Rebind**\n   - Update worker roster/runbooks to canonical paths\n6. **Operationalize**\n   - Schedule safe recurring checks and status output\n\n## Inputs\n- Local root: `C:\\Users\\tonyb\\.openclaw\\workspace`\n- Mirror root A: `G:\\My Drive\\openclaw-workspace-main`\n- Mirror root B: `G:\\My Drive\\openclaw-full-main`\n\n## Outputs\n- `ops/FULL_INVENTORY_REPORT.md`\n- `ops/PROJECT_CANONICAL_MAP.md`\n- `runbooks/WORKER_RECOVERY_PLAN.md`\n- `ops/TASK_BACKLOG_PRIORITIZED.md`\n- Prompt/task library under `prompts/`\n\n## Worker Loop (Daily)\n1. `scripts/run-daily-pipeline.ps1`\n2. Validate `job_pipeline/jobs_latest_summary.json`\n3. Write status to `deliverables/mission-control/mission_control_status.md`\n4. Log notable deltas to memory/runbook\n\n## Safe Failure Handling\n- If mirror unavailable: skip promotion; keep last good canonical state.\n- If staged content incomplete: retry hydration, do not overwrite canonical.\n- If worker script fails: capture error logs; create backlog item with repro command.\n\n## Non-Destructive Policy\n- Always use copy-first promotion.\n- No cleanup deletes during rebuild window.\n- Archive snapshots before any major copy pass.\n"},"partialJson":"{\"path\":\"C:\\\\Users\\\\tonyb\\\\.openclaw\\\\workspace\\\\runbooks\\\\WORKFLOW_BLUEPRINT_V1.md\",\"content\":\"# WORKFLOW BLUEPRINT V1\\n\\n## Intent\\nCreate a repeatable, safe rebuild workflow for project/worker continuity without destructive operations.\\n\\n## Workflow Graph (V1)\\n1. **Inventory (Read-only)**\\n   - Scan local + mirrors\\n   - Emit inventory report\\n2. **Canonical Mapping**\\n   - Select canonical roots\\n   - Label all duplicates as source/legacy\\n3. **Staging Recovery (Copy-only)**\\n   - Pull from chosen mirror to staging\\n   - Validate file counts and key manifests\\n4. **Promotion (Copy-only)**\\n   - Copy from staging to canonical project roots\\n5. **Worker Rebind**\\n   - Update worker roster/runbooks to canonical paths\\n6. **Operationalize**\\n   - Schedule safe recurring checks and status output\\n\\n## Inputs\\n- Local root: `C:\\\\Users\\\\tonyb\\\\.openclaw\\\\workspace`\\n- Mirror root A: `G:\\\\My Drive\\\\openclaw-workspace-main`\\n- Mirror root B: `G:\\\\My Drive\\\\openclaw-full-main`\\n\\n## Outputs\\n- `ops/FULL_INVENTORY_REPORT.md`\\n- `ops/PROJECT_CANONICAL_MAP.md`\\n- `runbooks/WORKER_RECOVERY_PLAN.md`\\n- `ops/TASK_BACKLOG_PRIORITIZED.md`\\n- Prompt/task library under `prompts/`\\n\\n## Worker Loop (Daily)\\n1. `scripts/run-daily-pipeline.ps1`\\n2. Validate `job_pipeline/jobs_latest_summary.json`\\n3. Write status to `deliverables/mission-control/mission_control_status.md`\\n4. Log notable deltas to memory/runbook\\n\\n## Safe Failure Handling\\n- If mirror unavailable: skip promotion; keep last good canonical state.\\n- If staged content incomplete: retry hydration, do not overwrite canonical.\\n- If worker script fails: capture error logs; create backlog item with repro command.\\n\\n## Non-Destructive Policy\\n- Always use copy-first promotion.\\n- No cleanup deletes during rebuild window.\\n- Archive snapshots before any major copy pass.\\n\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.3-codex","usage":{"input":200,"output":493,"cacheRead":31232,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":31925,"cost":{"input":0.00035,"output":0.006902,"cacheRead":0.0054656,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.012717599999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773082886334}}
